import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0):

    v1 = jnp.subtract(x0, v0)
    v2 = jnp.multiply(x0, x0)
    v3 = jnp.multiply(v0, v2)

    v5 = jnp.maximum(x0, v0)
